o our knowledge of Roman defenses in the third and fourth centuries of the Common Era, along the trade route that traversed the southern Arava and on the eastern frontier of the Empire.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 0aExcavations (Archaeology)xIsraelxYoṭvatah. 0aExcavations (Archaeology)zIsraelzYoṭvatah. 0aExcavationszIsraelzYotvatah. 0aFortification, RomanxIsraelxYoṭvatah. 0aFortification, RomanzIsraelzYoṭvatah. 0aRomansxIsraelxYoṭvatah. 0aRomanszIsraelzYoṭvatah. 7aHISTORY / Ancient / General.2bisacsh1 aDavies, Gwyn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aElkins, Nathan T., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHalbmaier, Rebecca, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMagness, Jodi, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aMagness, Jodi, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRamsay, Jennifer, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRatzlaff, Alexandra, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSwan, Carolyn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPenn State University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311074525240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781575063621zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781575063621423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781575063621.jpg  a978-3-11-074525-2  Penn State University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_CL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK